    "title": "Workspace-backed manager-worker coordination",
    "status": "completed",
    "objective": "Develop a truthful manager-worker operating model for Pi Loom in which workers are ephemeral workspaces, managers supervise and consolidate bounded execution across those workspaces, and the resulting system composes cleanly with plans, tickets, Ralph, critique, and documentation.",
